      "raw_text": "BOISE, Idaho, Sept. 6.-The mo-\nton for change OIL venue. filed by\nthe state in the case of Steve\nAdams, charged with the murder\nof Fred Tyler, was resisted by the\ndefense today by barrow claiming\nthe act of legislature giving the\nstate the right to ask for change of\nvenue in criminal cases Is uncon-\nstitutional.\n\n\nbarrow said in his argument that\nthe law was passed for the purpose\nOF convicting Meyer Haywood,\nPettibone and Adams. The motion\nwas taken under advisement."
